        "El conjunto de datos contiene las siguientes varaibles\n",
        "\n",
        "- GRCODE: Código  de la compañía\n",
        "- GRNAME\n",
        "- AccidentYear\n",
        "- DevelopmentYear\n",
        "- DevelopmentLag\n",
        "- IncurLoss_C\n",
        "- CumPaidLoss_C\n",
        "- BulkLoss_C\n",
        "- EarnedPremDIR_C\n",
        "- EarnedPremCeded_C\n",
        "- EarnedPremNet_C\n",
